commitResults.messageTitle: Ensure attended student is saved to addressbook.json

commitResults.messageBody:
Bug details:
  When loading from JSON:
  1. Students A and B are added to the class
  2. tuitionClass.addSession() calls new
  ClassSession(this, ...) (line 224 in
  TuitionClass.java)
  3. The ClassSession constructor calls
  initializeAttendance() which adds ALL current
  students (A and B) to attendance as absent
  4. Then we try to restore attendance from JSON
   (which only saved Student A)

The fix:
    Settle attendance records first before adding students in.
    tuitionClass starts off with 0 students, so addSession() will not
    add any students as absent.
    After consolidating saved attendance records, then add students to
    the class.
